  "practicalInfo": {
    "gettingThere": "Nearest airport: U-Tapao Pattaya (UTP) with some budget flights. Most travelers fly to Bangkok Suvarnabhumi (BKK) then take a bus or taxi (2h, $10-20 by bus). Private transfer ~$40.",
    "localTransport": "Baht buses (songthaew) circle the city for 10 THB flat. Grab app available. Scooter rental $8-10/day. Walking Street and beach road walkable.",
